# NOTE: the trained artifacts in models/ (model.joblib, metrics.json,
# model_card.md) are intentionally committed so the deployed app loads instantly
# and reliably (Streamlit Community Cloud cold-starts on every wake — retraining
# there would mean a multi-minute spinner). scikit-learn is pinned in
# requirements.txt so the committed pickle always loads. Regenerate any time
# with `python -m src.train`.

